Day 17 (Wednesday): The ExoCore Philosophy
Hook: Why every professional needs a Personal Operating System.

Body: I am developing ExoCore Systems as a parent brand for building reliable operating systems for businesses. CRABuddy is a direct "sibling" to my other project, PrepFlow OS, which serves the meal prep industry.

Whether you are a food entrepreneur or a Senior CRA, the core problem is the same: you need a reliable infrastructure to handle the logistics so you can focus on the mission. CRABuddy is the specialized "exoskeleton" designed to support the clinical research professional.

