Hook: Think of CRABuddy as the personal CRM for your CRA career.

Body: I love using popular app and tech examples because they resonate with the practical problems we face. Just as Salesforce manages customer relationships, CRABuddy manages your site relationships and professional achievements.

My interest is in building tools that feel as intuitive as the consumer tech we use every day. We work in a high-tech industry; it’s time our personal professional tools caught up with the SaaS standards of 2026.

