Day 20 (Saturday): Overcoming the "Start" Barrier
Hook: I almost didn’t build this because I didn't feel "successful enough" to start.

Body: Last year, I initiated an astrological analysis to align my business and money mindset. I identified a core belief that was holding me back: the feeling that I wasn't "successful enough" to launch my own venture.

Graduating from The Hatchery Chicago incubator program helped me realize that "sense" comes from doing. Whether you are launching a new app or pushing for a Senior II role, don’t let the feeling of "not being there yet" stop you from building the system that will take you there.

Hashtags: #Entrepreneurship #Mindset #TheHatcheryChicago #CRAEvolution

